EPISODE INFORMATION

 Las Vegas
 #3.02: Fake the Money and Run
 Monday September 26, 2005 (runtime: 60 mins)
 
 Category    : Drama                                                        
 Writers     : Gardner Stern                                                
 Director    : Tim Matheson                                                 
 Guest Stars : Dean Napolitano, Dennis Rodman, Paul Anka, Mary Castro,      
 Guest Stars : Christina Cindrich, Will Collyer, Nate Torrence, Rachael     
 Guest Stars : Leigh Cook                                                   

 The casino has reopened. Ed and Mike work on a case of counterfeit casino  
 chips. Per his accountant’s suggestion, Danny must sell his father’s house.
 Later, Danny’s accountant is part of a poker game where one of the players 
 is a man who robbs one of the casino’s guests. Monica Mancuso, the new     
 owner, wants a dealer to be fired because he keeps dealing winning hands to
 the players.                                                               

